<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥١٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١٨٩٧ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ:</span> فِي الرَّجُلِ يُمَلِّكُ امْرَأَتَهُ أَمْرَهَا فَتَرُدُّهُ إِلَيْهِ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ بِشَيْءٍ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>